Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎NETFLIX 出品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你覺得我打偏了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think I missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎瞧…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎打偏了10厘米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Off by four inches. …for the generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎嘿 你干什么 這些是我要買的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, what do you think you're doin'? I wanted those.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好的 盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gotcha, Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎…還有所謂的支付贖金\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}…and alleged ransom payments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們過去沒有 ‎我重復一遍 沒有通過武器交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We did not, repeat, did not trade weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎或其他方式來交換人質 ‎將來也不會這樣做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or anything else for hostages, nor will we.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎里根總統談及與伊朗的緊張關系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}President Reagan addressing the heightened tensions with Iran in the country's 1953 coup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎嘿 盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hey, Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎其他新聞 羅杰斯委員會的報告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In other news, pages from the Rogers Commission's report
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎調查了太空穿梭機挑戰者號災難 ‎讓美國宇航局備受抨擊…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}on the Space Shuttle Challenger disaster, with NASA under fire…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你為大風暴做好準備了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You, uh, ready for the big storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我要提款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Makin' a withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎今天要取多少錢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, uh, how much will you be taking out today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎有多少取多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, whatever's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎…沒有伊朗的配合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without Iran's cooperation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們無法結束波斯灣戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we cannot bring an end to the Persian Gulf War.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎沒有伊朗的…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Without Iran's…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎那…是很大一筆錢呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-There's a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我知道啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎錢就是我存進去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the one who put it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎如果您想打電話 ‎請先投幣25美分 然后再撥號\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you'd like to place a call, please deposit 25 cents before dialing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎如需幫助 請掛斷后重新致電\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you need help, please hang up and try your call again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎蘭金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rankin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎下午好 盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Afternoon, Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎賈克斯心情很好嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jax is in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我不禁在想 ‎是不是因為打獵很刺激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't help but wonder if the spark of the hunt
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎所以才讓它興奮得不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hasn't got him all worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不太可能 現在不是打獵的季節\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unlikely. It isn't hunting season.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎那鹿一定是突然冒出來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deer must have just bolted out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎迅雷不及掩耳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Happened so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我很高興你和賈克斯安全出來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm glad you and Jax came out of it okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你應該給自己買一條銅手鏈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, you ought to get yourself one of these copper bracelets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-漂亮 ‎-我侄女在大陸給我買的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Pretty. -My niece got it for me on the mainland.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎其中一個裝著好夢安睡環\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of those stores, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎還有水晶之類的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with the dream catchers and crystals and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我還笑她來著 但我對天發誓 ‎現在我的關節炎好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I laughed at her. But I swear to God, I barely feel the arthritis anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我又開始釣魚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm fishin' again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎戴著這玩意兒小心別被雷劈了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Careful you don't get struck by lightning wearin' that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎早上好 盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Oh, that's right. Mornin', Lou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我喜歡…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這是惡劣天氣預警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a severe weather watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎西北太平洋近年來最大的一次風暴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The biggest storm the Pacific Northwest has seen in years
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎預計將于今天入夜后來襲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is expected to make landfall early this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎請各位居民盡量待在家里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Residents are encouraged to stay in their homes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎做好準備 屆時會出現電力中斷 ‎低洼地區會有洪澇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and be prepared for downed power lines and flooding in low-lying areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎開往圣胡安群島的渡輪也已暫停服務\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ferry service to the San Juan Islands has also been suspended
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎重開時間另行通知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until further notice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎因為風暴將直接吹襲本區域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as the area is directly in the storm's path.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她跑哪兒去了呢 我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where could she be? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她不在這棵樹下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's not under this tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎（價真五金店）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她不在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's not over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她藏得真好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, she's so good at hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎一定得找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gotta find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎也許她在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe she's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好 我去那里看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I'm gonna check there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎抓到你啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I got you! -I got you! I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你都沒有說“小兔子”的暗號\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You didn't say the code! Little Rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎再來一次嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我說了不行 小薇 來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said no, Vee. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎把釘子遞給我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pass me a nail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎媽媽 你覺得 ‎爸爸會很快找到寶藏嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom, do you think Daddy's gonna find the treasure soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎已經兩年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我不知道 小薇 他應該很快會找到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know, Vee. I bet he's real close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎那爸爸會回家嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then is Daddy gonna come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎知道嗎 風暴似乎還要過會兒才來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, the storm looks like it's a while away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們或許可以再玩一次躲貓貓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We could probably fit in another game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:09:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我打賭你撐不過三分鐘 ‎就會被我找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I bet you can't make it past three minutes before I find you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-我可以的 ‎-我覺得你撐不過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Oh, I can. -Oh, I don't think you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好吧 我看看 準備好了嗎 預備…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right. Let me see. Ready? Set…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-游戲開始 ‎-游戲開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Game on! -Game on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎一\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎二\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}two…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎三\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}three…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎四\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}four…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎五 六\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}five… six…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎七…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seven…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-嘿 盧 ‎-房租 明天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hey, Lou. -Rent. Tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我知道 聽我說 ‎我得為風暴準備食品物資\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. Listen, now, I had to lay in supplies for the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-能不能… ‎-不能延期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-So I was wondering whether-- -No extensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎明天 把錢放在里面桌子上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Tomorrow. Inside. On the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-不然放在信箱里會弄濕的 ‎-錢會付給你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll get wet in the mailbox. You'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你這人是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎明知道附近有小孩 ‎你為什么還要開這么快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why you gotta drive so goddamn fast? You know there's a child nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這世界不是游樂場 ‎教你的孩子要自己小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}World's not a playground. Teach your kid to look out for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎來吧 賈克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Jax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-嘿 ‎-進去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hey. -Go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-媽媽  ‎-小薇 進去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No, Mom! -Vee, go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Everything o-- okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎別跺腳 小姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And no stomping, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不 不用了 謝謝你 克里斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No. We're fine. Thanks, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-你還好嗎  ‎-還好 我只是累了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You doin' all right? -Yeah, I'm just tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧還在讓你煩惱嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is Lou still bein' a pain in your ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我跟你說過這事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I told you about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-你不記得了 我們… ‎-不記得了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, you don't… you don't remember? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎聽我說 我們當時都喝醉了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}-Look, we were both pretty drunk, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-是啊 ‎-對 顯然如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Yeah. Yeah. -Clearly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎因為我都不記得我說過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}'cause I… I don't remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我記得你使出了吃奶的勁兒 ‎在唱“宛如處女”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do remember you singing "Like A Virgin" at the top of your lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎請你發誓不告訴別人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, please swear you'll never tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不然呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不然…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎媽 我找不到河馬先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom! I can't find Mr. Hippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎嘿 你有沒有…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hey, have you, um…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎媽 幫我找把它找出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Mom, help me find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你找機會跟小薇談過了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you had a chance to talk to Vee yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎關于她爸的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About her dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-我能搭個便車嗎  ‎-當然可以 上車吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Any way I could get a ride? -Yeah, of course. Get in here. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎倒霉的租賃車壞掉了 ‎你真是幫了我一個大忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry about that. Oh, damn rental car broke down on me. You're a lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎天啊 我把你的座位都弄濕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, jeez, I'm-- I'm gettin' your seat all soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎別擔心 得虧是我開車經過看見了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry about it, man. I'm just glad I passed you when I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎風暴天會很危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The storm's gonna be gnarly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎（《論死亡與臨終》）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好深奧啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heavy reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎對 給我一個朋友買的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I bought it for a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她的前夫三個月前去世了 ‎她很難接受現實 所以…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her ex died three months ago, and she's just-- she's havin' a hard time facin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎明白了 你想幫她面對現實吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see. And you wanna help her face it, right? Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-因為你想比做朋友更進一步  ‎-不 聽我說 我只是…她有個孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause you wanna be more than just friends? Oh, look, I just-- She has a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她想慢慢來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She wants to take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎哦 我喜歡這個樂隊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh! I love this band.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-杰夫波卡羅是個很厲害的人 ‎-哦 是的 他是最棒的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Jeff Porcaro's the man. -Oh, yeah. He's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎搞什么 操\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck! What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎（大學資金）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎（爸爸 小薇）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Vee…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇 看著我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vee, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你之前問過爸爸的事 對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know when you were asking about Daddy earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎怎么說呢…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, um…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎寶貝 他…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Baby, he, um…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他很愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He loves you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他心里一直在掛念你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he thinks about you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你在做什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are we making?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-友誼手鏈 ‎-哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Friendship bracelets. -Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我想做一條友誼手鏈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanna make a friendship bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這個是給盧的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one is for Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你在給盧做手鏈 為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're making a bracelet for Lou? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我喜歡盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我知道你不喜歡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I know you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不 我喜歡啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好吧 我其實不喜歡盧 ‎但是你為什么喜歡她呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. I actually don't like Lou. But why do you like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎因為賈克斯喜歡她 而我喜歡賈克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, Jax likes her, and I like Jax.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我向來不是話多的人 ‎我就長話短說了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I've never been one for many words, so I'll keep this short."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎房子歸你了 拿去賣掉吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"The house is yours. Sell it."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎冰箱的肉夠賈克斯吃一個月 ‎還有給你一些現金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"There's a month's worth of meat for Jax in the freezer, and some cash for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我做的一些決定 你永遠都不會理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"There are certain decisions I made that you will never understand."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎但那都是過去的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"But that's all in the past now."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎人生可能會很殘酷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Life can be cruel."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎有些事我很擅長 ‎但有些事我做得一塌糊涂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"What made me great at some things made me lousy at others."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我希望我能說 ‎自己的所作所為帶來了好的結果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I wish I could say that some good came from what I did."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎事實上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"In truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我讓世界變成了更危險的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I left the world a more dangerous place."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎現在該睡啦 好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Bedtime, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-河馬先生  ‎-我累壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Mr. Hippo! -I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎來吧 河馬先生 晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Mr. Hippo. -Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我好熱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'm hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我也很熱 ‎但很快就涼快了 因為下雨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, now I'm hot too. But you'll be cold soon because it's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎只是風而已 寶貝 別害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's just the wind, baby. Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我沒有怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-好的 ‎-你害怕嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Okay. -Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-你今晚想跟我睡嗎  ‎-如果你想 我就跟你睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Do you wanna sleep with me tonight? -Oh, if you need me to, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我想讓你跟我睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I think I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit, shit, shit, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}-Vee…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-說話注意點 ‎-該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Watch your mouth. -Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我要去把斷電器打上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just gonna go flip the breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我馬上回來 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be right back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是你嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎克里斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh! Vee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不 小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! Vee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:22:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vee! Vee! Vee! Vee? Vee!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:22:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-電話呢  ‎-搞什么鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Where's your phone? -What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死的電話在哪 我得打給警長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's your goddamn phone? I gotta call the sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-媽的 操  ‎-別急 出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-God damn it! Fuck! -Slow down. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇不見了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Vee's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.08,0:23:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你又讓她跑開了 她走不了多遠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What, you let her wander off again? -She's not gonna get far in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.58,0:23:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不 她爸爸把她帶走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No, no, no. -Her father took her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Her father?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他來了 他怎么會在這里\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's… he's here. How the hell is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎等等 你看到他了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold on. You saw him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.37,0:23:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎沒有 我…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.41,0:23:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他應該是死了 但是他找到了我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He… he's supposed to be dead, but he found us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.45,0:23:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我以為擺脫他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-- I thought we were free of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他還殺了克里斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He killed Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你的鑰匙呢  ‎車子發動不了 我得去找警長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are your keys? The car won't start. I gotta get to the sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-我來開車 ‎-好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'll drive. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎糟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.58,0:23:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No, no, no, no, no! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-怎么了  ‎-快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What's wrong? -Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:23:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.33,0:24:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你怎么知道會爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ho-- how did you know it was gonna blow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.83,0:24:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎炸彈就是會爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bombs tend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.41,0:24:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry about that, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.08,0:24:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我還沒做完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turns out I'm not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.58,0:24:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎炸彈 盧 ‎這說明他一直在計劃這件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A bomb? It means he's been plannin' this, Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.70,0:24:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們需要更多支援 我們得去找警長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We gotta get more help. We need to get to the sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.20,0:24:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎沒法去找他 沒有車 電話也壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't get to him. No cars. Phones are down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.58,0:24:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們在城外十幾公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're ten miles outside of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.12,0:24:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎每耽誤一秒 ‎你孩子就走遠一步 我得去追蹤他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your kid's gettin' further away by the second. I have to track 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.91,0:24:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.33,0:25:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你追蹤他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Track 'em? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.62,0:25:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎去拿電池 在廚房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get batteries. Kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.45,0:25:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你不了解情況 菲利普以前當過兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't understand. Philip was a Green Beret.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.50,0:25:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他在中美洲做了可怕的事 ‎因此還被通緝了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wanted for some terrible shit that he did in Central America.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.45,0:25:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是戰爭罪什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}War crimes kind of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.12,0:25:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我看了法庭手稿 他折磨俘虜來作樂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw the court transcripts. He was torturing hostages for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.54,0:25:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他訓練有素\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's highly trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.87,0:25:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是個炸彈專家 ‎媽的 我們可不是他的對手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An explosives expert. Well, we're no match for him, Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.70,0:25:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們需要專業的救援 ‎光憑你和你家狗是不行的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need professional help. You and the dog ain't gonna cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.25,0:25:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他從你的拖車里拿走了什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did he take anything from your trailer?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.83,0:25:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎拿走了小薇最喜歡的 ‎河馬先生玩偶 還有一條毯子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her-- her favorite stuffy, Mr. Hippo. -And a-- a blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.95,0:25:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他想讓她舒服一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He wants her comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.04,0:25:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他只想讓她保持安靜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wants her quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.08,0:25:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎正在翻修\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Renovations.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.50,0:26:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎警察試圖逮捕他時 ‎他炸毀了自己的公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When they tried to arrest him, he blew his apartment up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.79,0:26:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎警察也發了死亡證明 ‎他怎么可能還活著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They sent a death certificate. How the hell could he still be alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.95,0:26:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎氟烷 會讓人昏睡的氣體\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Halothane. Sleeping gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.70,0:26:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你沒被迷暈 算你走運\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're lucky it didn't knock you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.54,0:26:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他用東西把她拉著走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's pullin' her in somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.58,0:26:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他要是想帶小薇離開島 ‎事情就更復雜了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he gets her off the island, this will get a lot messier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.79,0:26:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎飛機場和渡輪都關了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Airport and ferry are closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.66,0:26:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎要坐私人游艇 他就得去海岸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Private vessel. He's headed to the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.87,0:26:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他有領先優勢 ‎我得抓緊了 你待在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's got a head start. I gotta move fast. Stay here.  
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.41,0:26:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴風雨過后  再進城\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The storm clears, head into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.91,0:26:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你看到第一個房子時 就打電話給警長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First house you see, call the sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.70,0:26:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-喂 你要去哪里  ‎-去找我的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hey, where are you goin'? -To find my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.20,0:26:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你不知道自己在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.75,0:27:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎如果你拖慢我的速度 ‎我就把你扔下不管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you slow me down, I will leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.66,0:27:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎賈克斯 繼續走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jax. Right on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.62,0:27:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎什么都看不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't see shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.04,0:27:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們很接近了 正在穿過山脊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're close. We're clearing the ridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.62,0:27:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們馬上就到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be there shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.08,0:27:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死的一群白癡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Fuckin' idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.95,0:28:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不 沒關系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No, no, no. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.66,0:28:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我知道好久沒見了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.00,0:28:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎也許這能喚起你的記憶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe this'll jog your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.33,0:28:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這個是教堂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here's the church…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.00,0:28:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這是尖頂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here's the steeple…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.08,0:28:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎把它打開 然后是…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Open it up and…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.16,0:28:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.16,0:28:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎對 是的 是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, it is. It's-- it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.87,0:28:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是我 寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's me, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.25,0:28:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你探完險回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You came back from your adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.08,0:28:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.79,0:28:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我還給你帶了禮物呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And… and I even brought you a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.95,0:28:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是在寶藏堆里找到的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it part of the treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.45,0:29:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎寶藏 對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, treasure? Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.75,0:29:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎沒錯 當然是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, it sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.37,0:29:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎而且你和我要一起 ‎去一趟屬于我們的探險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And… you and I are gonna go on our own adventure together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.91,0:29:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎媽媽在哪兒 她跟我們一起去嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Mo-- Where's Mommy? Is she coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.62,0:29:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎對 她當然要去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, of course she is. Of course she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.83,0:29:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我給她留了紙條和提示 讓她跟上來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I left her a note and some clues to follow us,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.54,0:29:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她晚點會跟我們匯合的 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she's gonna meet up with us after, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.91,0:29:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎別急嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh-- Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.83,0:29:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你要說什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.29,0:29:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎謝謝 爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.08,0:29:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.00,0:29:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎能收到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.33,0:29:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎收到 快上線 能聽到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Get on radio. -Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.00,0:29:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好吧 我還有一件事要處理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-All right, I've gotta do one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.25,0:29:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎然后你就要和我一起開始探險了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then you and I are gonna start our adventure together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.75,0:29:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎所以你戴上這個 好了 就是這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}See, you put these on… All right, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.20,0:29:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.33,0:30:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.12,0:31:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你看到什么了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.25,0:31:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-你認識他們  ‎-托尼和格里 是菲利普的戰友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You know them? -Tony and Gerry. They served with Philip.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.25,0:31:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-他們就跟菲利普一樣狠毒 ‎-來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're just as vicious as he is. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.87,0:32:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎趴下別動 你的外套就是一個活靶子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay down. Your jacket might as well have a target painted on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.33,0:32:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們等著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-We wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.04,0:32:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎萬一這只是聲東擊西呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Suppose this is just a distraction?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.91,0:32:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好爭取更多時間讓他帶著小薇離開 ‎他就喜歡搞這種鬼把戲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Buying him more time to get away with Vee. It's the kind of game he likes to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.62,0:32:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎拿閃亮的東西在你面前晃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Danglin' somethin' shiny in front of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.58,0:32:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎然后他趁你不備 給你腦袋一悶棍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you don't notice when he's about to bash you over your goddamn head.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.83,0:32:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你會用槍嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know how to use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.45,0:32:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我會 我離開他之后去上課學過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mmm, yeah. -I took lessons after I left him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.83,0:32:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好的 我得去看一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-All right, I'm gonna go have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.95,0:32:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎如果有人離得太近 就用這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If anybody gets too close, use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.08,0:32:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎直接戳眼睛 眼瞎的人沒法要你的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go for the eyes. A man can't kill what he can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.12,0:32:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-你在哪里學的這些東西  ‎-女童子軍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-How do you know all this? -Girl Scouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.91,0:32:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎賈克斯 待著別動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jax. Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.41,0:33:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這種鬼天氣 沒人想跟著他過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, no one's gonna follow him in this shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.29,0:33:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎感覺這又是一次菲利普的蹩腳游戲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm telling you, this feels like another one of Philip's fucked-up games.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.50,0:33:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎有人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.08,0:33:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不好意思 我把這里都轉了個遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, excuse me. I'm completely turned around out here. I--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.33,0:33:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我在找我家的狗 可憐的小家伙…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I… I was looking for my dog. The poor little guy--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.20,0:33:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-我沒看到狗 ‎-好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I haven't seen any dogs. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.12,0:33:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你有電話可以借給我用嗎 我只想…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do… do you have a phone I could use? -I just want--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.45,0:33:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎就你一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.62,0:33:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎很不幸 是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Unfortunately. Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.00,0:34:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎聽我說 我感覺自己 ‎沒法再撐三個小時走路回家了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I-- I don't think I can make it the three hours back home, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.70,0:34:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不過 要是能歇歇腳就好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if I could just rest and get my… my bearings?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.33,0:34:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.08,0:34:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好吧 只能待兩分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Okay. Just two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.33,0:34:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎非常感謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.75,0:34:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.08,0:34:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎多謝你的善心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, bless your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.37,0:34:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎早上好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.87,0:34:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她的狗跑丟了 被雨淋濕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She lost her dog, man. She's soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.87,0:34:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎只要讓我的血液循環起來就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just need to get my blood movin' again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.25,0:34:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎天啊 外面的風暴真是厲害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My goodness. Quite a storm out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.66,0:34:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你叫什么名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.83,0:34:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎哦 抱歉 我叫瑪莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, sorry, I'm-- I'm Martha.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.12,0:34:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎弗萊明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Flemming.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.50,0:34:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎但你們可能認識我丈夫 ‎他上班的地方在…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you might know my husband, Gordon. -He works at the--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.91,0:34:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不認識\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.45,0:35:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎來 坐一下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here. Why don't you grab a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.79,0:35:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-讓冰冷的腳休息一下 ‎-那就太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Give those cold feet a break. -They sure could use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.83,0:35:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.91,0:35:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎非常感謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.08,0:35:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你在島上待了很久嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So… been on this island long?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.33,0:35:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎32年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Oh, 32 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.41,0:35:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不知道這有什么好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I don't get the appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.83,0:35:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎過來一趟也麻煩 天氣又糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a pain in the ass to get to. -Weather's shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.08,0:35:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎得慢慢習慣才行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an acquired taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.54,0:35:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我就很喜歡這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.00,0:35:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我倒覺得是個藏身的好地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Good place to hide, I reckon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.29,0:35:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎得了吧 托尼 放松點 她只是個老太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Tony, relax. She's just an old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.37,0:35:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎（來自德黑蘭的愛）
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.16,0:35:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這湯聞著好香啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The soup smells so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.66,0:35:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這里真舒服 又暖和\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So nice and warm in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.54,0:36:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎那一定是我家賈克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That must be my Jax.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.16,0:36:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎坐下 瑪莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sit down, Martha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.95,0:37:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他要帶她去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is he taking her?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.37,0:37:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎快說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.79,0:37:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他要帶她去哪里\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}…is he taking her?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.37,0:37:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎老鷹灣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eagle Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.87,0:37:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎然后呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then where?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.08,0:37:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.62,0:37:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我發誓 我只知道這些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I swear. That's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.12,0:38:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你要開槍打我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gonna shoot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.08,0:38:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎事態\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Things, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.70,0:38:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎更嚴峻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}escalated.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.20,0:38:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎賈克斯 我是怎么跟你說的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jax. What'd I tell you about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.75,0:38:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎在你殺格里之前 ‎他說了關于小薇的線索嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gerry, he say anything about Vee before you killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.62,0:38:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎一個字都沒說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.91,0:39:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎給你 把這個拿出去 仔細翻一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here. Take this outside. Go through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.50,0:39:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎喂 拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.70,0:39:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個東西關掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turn that thing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.00,0:39:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-我們也許能聯系到警長 ‎-這種天氣就別指望了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-We might be able to reach the sheriff. -Not in this weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.08,0:39:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎更有可能會引起菲利普的注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More likely it'll tip off Philip.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.75,0:39:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-哪個頻道才是… ‎-別跟我爭辯 快放下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What channel would the emergency-- -Don't argue with me. Leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.91,0:39:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎難以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.33,0:40:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你知道 我也參加過女童子軍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I was in the Girl Scouts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.12,0:40:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我拿到了射箭徽章 ‎交到了筆友 學會了急救\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got my archery badge, pen pal, first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.87,0:40:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎但是他們沒教過徒手搏擊 ‎或者拿家用物品來殺人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There wasn't one for hand-to-hand combat or murder with household objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.29,0:40:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是嗎 那肯定是我服役的時候學的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really? Must've just been my troop, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.29,0:40:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你隸屬哪支部隊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What branch of the military were you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.79,0:40:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎中情局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.00,0:40:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎做了26年的外勤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}26 years in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.91,0:40:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎間諜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.41,0:40:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-還真沒想到 ‎-要是被你猜到 我這特務就太菜了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Wouldn't have guessed that. -Be a shit spy if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.29,0:40:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎來吧 賈克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come on, Jax.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.00,0:41:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.08,0:41:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我在呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.20,0:41:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我要尿尿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.91,0:41:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你能忍一忍嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Can-- can you hold it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.41,0:41:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎忍不住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Nuh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.75,0:41:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.75,0:41:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎稍微歇一會兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Short break.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.83,0:42:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎有人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.66,0:42:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎見鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.29,0:42:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎喂 有人在嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, hello. Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.04,0:42:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.00,0:42:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好了 快點 小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, come on, Vee.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.45,0:42:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vee?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.70,0:42:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vee!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.62,0:43:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎讓我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me see?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.41,0:43:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是的 它的翅膀受傷了 小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. No, he's got-- he's got a bad wing, Vee.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.79,0:43:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.00,0:43:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你要知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.12,0:43:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎有時候在大自然里\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}sometimes, in nature, when a…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.83,0:43:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎當一個生物受傷了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}creature's damaged…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.75,0:43:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎其實你也救不了它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's nothing you can do to save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.37,0:43:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎就好像它注定要死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's almost like they were meant to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.66,0:43:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎但也許它只是累了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But maybe he's just tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.50,0:43:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎也許吧 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.95,0:43:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎來 我把它放到這上面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh… Here. We'll put him right up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.70,0:43:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-好了 來吧 ‎-等等 我還沒尿尿呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-All right. Come on. -Wait, I haven't peed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.62,0:44:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎快點 小薇 得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Vee. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.12,0:44:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎媽的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.33,0:44:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-操 ‎-哪里疼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Fuck. -What's hurtin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.29,0:44:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不疼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.29,0:44:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎快點 我們得繼續走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. We gotta keep movin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.16,0:45:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎媽的 開什么玩笑 見鬼 我操\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Fucking kidding me! Damn it. Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.25,0:45:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎嗨 得下來自己走了 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi. We have to walk now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.08,0:45:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-我需要休息一下 ‎-啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I need a break. -Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.95,0:45:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我需要休息 暖暖身子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need a break to warm up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.83,0:45:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎沒時間了 盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No time, Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.16,0:45:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他也會休息 ‎從他留下的蹤跡就看得出來 來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He takes breaks too. I can tell by the tracks. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.91,0:46:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.83,0:46:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎可惡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.25,0:46:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我不覺得太冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not too cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.25,0:46:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.62,0:46:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.37,0:46:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你帶傷走了這么久 早該告訴我才對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You walked a long way on that. You should've said somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.54,0:46:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好讓你拋下我不管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And give you an excuse to abandon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.95,0:46:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-那是給我的嗎  ‎-不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that for me? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.33,0:46:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎能給我一點嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, can I have some?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.45,0:47:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.66,0:47:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你卻還是留下了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet you stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.50,0:47:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你早就該做點什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, should've done somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.20,0:48:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.12,0:48:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎謝謝你 盧 你這番話很有幫助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks, Lou. That's… very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.37,0:48:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我是說你應該早點離開他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just saying you could've left him sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.75,0:48:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你知道跟他這樣的人 ‎在一起是怎樣的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it you know about being with someone like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.79,0:48:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎所以或許不要當事后諸葛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So maybe don't tell me what I should have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.16,0:48:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我都不認得跟他在一起時的自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't recognize who I was with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.75,0:48:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎其實 我以為我可以治愈他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I actually felt I could fix him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.58,0:48:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你知道 我們最初認識時 他很愛我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, when we met, he was loving,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.91,0:48:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他很在乎我 但他的心支離破碎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}he was caring… But so broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.95,0:48:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎過去這么久了 ‎我還以為都是我一個人的錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For so long, I thought… thought it was all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.25,0:48:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我以為…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.04,0:48:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎為什么我會讓他失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Why am I failing him?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.70,0:49:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎為什么我的愛還不夠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why isn't my love enough?"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.33,0:49:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.62,0:49:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎那個混蛋是個怪物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That son of a bitch is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.12,0:49:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不管是什么煉獄把他折磨成這副模樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever the hell made him this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.37,0:49:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎反正就算用盡全世界的愛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There ain't no amount of love in this entire world
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.33,0:49:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎都沒法拯救他這種人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's gonna be able to save that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.95,0:49:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他傷害過小薇嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He ever hurt Vee?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.95,0:49:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.62,0:49:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎還沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.12,0:49:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎每當他大發脾氣的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When he would get into his moods,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.37,0:49:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我就跟小薇小聲說：“游戲開始”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd whisper to her, "Game on,"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.37,0:49:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎然后她就會跑去躲起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she'd run and hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.08,0:49:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我居然把它變成了一個該死的游戲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Actually made it into a… a goddamn game.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.79,0:50:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你說這有多可悲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How pathetic is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.33,0:50:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他總是說 如果我帶走小薇 ‎他就會殺了我們兩個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He always said, if I took Vee away, he'd kill us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.83,0:50:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎所以你說吧 我當時該怎么辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Go on… Tell me what I should've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.95,0:50:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我想我倆都經歷了別人無法理解的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess we've all been through things other people will never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.87,0:50:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎漢娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.79,0:50:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們會把她救回來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll get her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.79,0:51:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.33,0:51:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit, shit, shit, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.95,0:51:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎慢慢來 保持平穩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Slow and steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.75,0:51:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎回家吧 賈克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Home, Jax.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.62,0:51:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不準跟我爭辯 回家 快去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No arguments. Home. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.45,0:51:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎見鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.58,0:52:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他到底是怎么帶著小薇一起過去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How the hell did he do this with Vee?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.54,0:52:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-得爬過去才行 ‎-該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gotta climb around it. Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.87,0:52:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎哇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.87,0:52:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.66,0:52:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我扶著你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.75,0:52:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.70,0:53:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.95,0:53:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.41,0:53:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎真會挑時候 媽的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not now. God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.16,0:53:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-盧 你怎么了  ‎-沒什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Lou, what's the matter? -Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.91,0:53:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Lou!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.00,0:54:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lou!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.37,0:54:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎謝天謝地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Oh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.79,0:54:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你讓我扶你起來就好了嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can help you if you just let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.87,0:54:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不需要你幫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.54,0:54:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎媽的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Oh, fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.54,0:54:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎起來 耽誤了一小時 得追上他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get up. We just lost an hour on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.41,0:55:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎喂 我叫你不要帶上這玩意兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, I told you to leave that behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.04,0:55:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎風暴過去了 ‎我要爬上那個山頂 試著連接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Storm's passed. I'm gonna climb up to that hilltop. -Try to connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.25,0:55:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎沒時間了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.41,0:55:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎見鬼 你別那么固執好嗎  ‎我們需要幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God damn it. Can you stop bein' so stubborn? We need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.54,0:55:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎沒人能幫我們 ‎我是你的唯一希望 現在繼續走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-There is no one who can help us. -Shit. -I'm all you've got. Now keep movin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.20,0:55:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-你為什么要幫我 盧  ‎-老鷹灣就在前面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Why are you helpin' me, Lou? -Huh? -Eagle Bay's just ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.00,0:55:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-別拖慢我的速度 ‎-見鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Don't slow me down. -God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.04,0:56:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們錯過了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We missed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.70,0:56:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎海浪這么洶涌 人員無法進出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one's comin' or goin' in water this rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.33,0:56:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎那他打算怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Then what's his plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.04,0:56:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.37,0:57:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Vee!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.45,0:57:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vee!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.37,0:57:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎漢娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.54,0:57:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-你把她帶到哪里去了  ‎-別喊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Where did you take her? -Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.87,0:57:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他這是在捉弄你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He's fucking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.04,0:57:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們可以就這樣耗一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can do this all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.45,0:57:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎也許你說得對 ‎我們可能確實需要幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe you're right. Maybe we do need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.08,0:57:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你回到山里去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go back to that hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.04,0:57:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎看看你能不能聯系上蘭金 ‎緊急服務在第16頻道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See if you can raise Rankin. Emergency services are channel 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.79,0:57:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎聯系到了之后回來這里跟我匯合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meet me back here when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.37,0:57:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎謝謝你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.29,0:57:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你打算怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.95,0:57:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要休息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.33,0:57:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.00,0:58:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎嘿 等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.75,0:58:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎可別一槍崩了自己的腦袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try not to blow your brains out.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.87,0:58:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎（永遠和你在一起 ）
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.87,0:58:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎（你照亮我的生活）
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.33,0:59:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.79,0:59:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎凍結在時間里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Frozen in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.66,0:59:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎永遠和你在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.66,0:59:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎還想再印一個嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wanna do another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.54,0:59:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你知道嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.29,0:59:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎世界各地的山洞里都有像這樣的手印\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that there are handprints like these in caves all over the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.08,0:59:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎等你和媽媽還有我都死了很久之后\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And long after you and Mommy and I are all dead…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.79,0:59:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這些手印還會在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}these handprints are still gonna be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.62,1:00:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎有人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.62,1:00:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎喂 有人能聽到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello? Can anyone hear me? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.83,1:01:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎有人聽到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can anybody hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.41,1:01:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.50,1:01:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你好 有人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, anybody?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.16,1:01:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-該死 -我是蘭金‎警長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-God damn it. -This is Sheriff Rankin.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.70,1:01:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰 結束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is this? Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.12,1:01:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎警長 蘭金警長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sheriff! Sheriff Rankin.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.95,1:01:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是--這是漢娜·道森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is-- this is Hannah Dawson.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.12,1:01:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-…被綁架了 ‎-綁架\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}…kidnapped. Kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.25,1:01:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漢娜 你能聽到我說話嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.45,1:01:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請重復一遍好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you repeat that, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.91,1:01:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh-- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.33,1:01:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒被她父親綁架了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My daughter was kidnapped by her father.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.79,1:01:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.25,1:01:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-盧阿德爾和我在一起 ‎-漢娜 你能確認情況嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lou Adell is with me… Hannah, can you please confirm?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.29,1:01:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-漢娜道森 你能聽到嗎  ‎-什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah Dawson? Can you hear me? What?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.70,1:01:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你再說一次好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Say that… say that again?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.20,1:01:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.75,1:01:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎警長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.87,1:01:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死 好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh fuck. Okay…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.75,1:01:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎可惡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.50,1:01:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎呼叫托瑞斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Torres, come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.08,1:01:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-警長 請講 ‎-聽著 我們有情況\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Go, Sheriff. -Listen, we got a situation.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.08,1:01:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎聽起來難以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is gonna sound a bit crazy,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.45,1:02:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎但是我想漢娜道森的女兒 ‎被她父親綁架了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I think Hannah Dawson's daughter has been kidnapped by… by her father.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.25,1:02:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.04,1:02:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎聽著 我們馬上把信息發布出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, let's put it on the wire, right away,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.79,1:02:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎以防女孩被帶離這座島\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in case she's taken off the island.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.25,1:02:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好吧 漢娜道森 薇道森和盧阿德爾 ‎她好像也提到了盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay? Hannah and Vee Dawson and Lou Adell. I think she mentioned Lou.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.20,1:03:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎放下槍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The guns.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.00,1:03:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎慢點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Slowly.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.50,1:04:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你好 菲利普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, Philip.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.83,1:04:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎別擔心她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.91,1:04:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我已經確保她會保持昏睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've made sure she'll sleep through this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.83,1:04:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎告訴我一件事 老實回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just tell me one thing. And be honest here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.70,1:04:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你為什么要出賣我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why'd you sell me out?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.79,1:04:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我知道你遲早會找到漢娜和小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew you'd track down Hannah and Vee sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.83,1:04:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我無法永遠保護她們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't gonna be able to protect them forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.75,1:04:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎保護她們 這一切都是因你而起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Protect them? All of this is happening because of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.37,1:05:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不是嗎 漢娜可能太天真了 ‎她沒想明白 但是我不傻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay? And Hannah may be too naive to-- to see it, but I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.79,1:05:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎漢娜不知道我是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah doesn't know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.66,1:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你連承認我是你兒子都還做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You still can't even admit I'm your son.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.00,1:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎菲利普 你打算做什么  ‎為什么要這樣你追我趕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what's the plan, Philip? Why the elaborate chase?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.25,1:05:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎為什么要讓我們追蹤你  ‎你并不想傷害你的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why let us track you? You don't wanna hurt your kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.79,1:05:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你知道嗎 那些人把我擄走時 ‎我年紀就跟小薇一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you know that Vee is the same age as I was when those-- those men took me?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.04,1:05:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是的 但他們就沒有 ‎像我現在這樣 對她這么溫柔了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but they weren't as nice as, uh… as I'm being to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.79,1:05:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這樣的相似程度 你不覺得很巧嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you appreciate that? The symmetry of that?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.29,1:05:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我以為我媽媽也會回來救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought my mommy was comin' back to save me, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.79,1:05:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎那是個陷阱 ‎要是我來救你的話 我倆都會被抓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a trap. If I'd tried to save you, they would have had us both.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.54,1:05:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎胡說 你只想保護自己的臥底身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bullshit. You wanted to maintain your cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.45,1:05:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我只是你執行任務的一枚棋子而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was a pawn for your mission. Nothin' else.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.70,1:05:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我救了你 我把你從伊朗救了出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I had you rescued. I got you out of Iran.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.50,1:05:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎那你怎么不跟我一起回來  ‎原因很簡單\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Then why didn't you come back with me? Here's why.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.12,1:06:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎因為你他媽的選擇了中情局 ‎而不是選擇自己的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you chose the fucking CIA over your own child.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.08,1:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎后來事情怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, how'd that work out for you? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.25,1:06:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎伊朗被你們搞得一團糟 ‎你們還做過比這更糟糕的事嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, did you guys fuck up anything worse than you fucked up Iran?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.54,1:06:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎然后 你偷走了我的妻子和孩子…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then you steal my wife and-- and my kid--
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.50,1:06:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她們跟我犯的錯無關 別牽扯上她們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah and Vee had nothing to do with my mistakes. Leave them out of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.50,1:06:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你就別給我上思想道德課了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, spare me the fuckin' morality lesson.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.66,1:06:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你早就放棄了這個權利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gave up that right a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.50,1:06:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎現在還不遲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.66,1:06:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你敢動一下 我就給你一槍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You move, I'mma put a bullet in you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.33,1:06:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎現在還不遲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.33,1:06:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎把小薇留給我 然后你走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave Vee with me and go.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.62,1:06:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我會把她們從你的蹤跡中抹去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll throw them off your trail.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.95,1:06:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎菲利普 聽我說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Philip, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.95,1:06:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你說得對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.79,1:06:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你小時候我沒保護好你 ‎現在就讓我做彌補吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't protect you when you were a kid. So let me do it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.91,1:06:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎閉嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.91,1:06:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎怎么 你想殺我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, you wanna kill me?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.54,1:06:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎動手吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.04,1:06:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你昨晚帶走小薇時 ‎我正拿著來復槍抵著自己腦袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before I knew you took Vee last night, I had my rifle pressed against my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.33,1:06:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我不怕死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not afraid to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.91,1:07:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你別總是打亂我的思緒 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You just can't stop messin' with my head, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.12,1:07:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我甚至不知道從何講起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kid, I wouldn't even know where to start.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.25,1:07:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我知道你把自己炸死了之后 ‎我就知道時機到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The minute I heard you blew yourself up, I knew it was time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.16,1:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我以為漢娜和小薇會很安全 ‎我的任務已經完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought Hannah and Vee were safe. My mission was complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.29,1:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎但你欺騙了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you tricked me there, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.50,1:07:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你向來都比我聰明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You always were smarter than me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.25,1:07:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你五歲時下象棋就比我厲害很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beat my ass at chess when you were five years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.33,1:07:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎記得嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.33,1:07:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我記得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.41,1:07:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎哦 菲利普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Philip.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.58,1:07:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你猜怎么著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.25,1:07:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這次要按我的游戲規則來玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For once, we're playin' my game.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.33,1:08:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是時候做個了結了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's time to end this legacy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.29,1:08:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好讓這一家子都擺脫痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put this whole family out of its misery.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.29,1:08:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎菲利普 你是她爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Philip, you're her father.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.20,1:08:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你也是我媽媽啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.08,1:09:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.12,1:09:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們會在燈塔等你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be waiting for you at the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.58,1:09:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎一定要帶漢娜一起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make sure you bring Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.50,1:09:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎別讓我們久等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't take too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.83,1:09:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎媽的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.79,1:10:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎只是想問問你情況怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just checking in on ya. How are you doing out there?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.79,1:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎副警長 進展如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Talk to me, Deputy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.87,1:10:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎在全境通緝布告里沒找到匹配\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Still no hits on the APBs.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.45,1:10:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎已把卡車上的炸彈告知了交通運輸部 ‎跟驗尸官匯報了尸體情況\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I notified ATF about the bomb in the truck and the coroner about the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.83,1:10:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎等天氣好轉 他們就會派隊伍過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're sending teams when the weather lets up.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.70,1:10:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎奧卡斯島警察局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Orcas Island Sheriff's Department.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.70,1:10:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是的 長官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.79,1:10:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎警長 是聯邦執法官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sheriff, it's the federal marshals.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.95,1:10:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我是蘭金 你是哪位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-This is Rankin. Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.29,1:10:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎警長 我是多米尼克科朗 ‎你收到傳真了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Sheriff, Dominick Crown here. Did you receive our facsimile transmission?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.75,1:10:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎收到了 我正拿在手里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I got it right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.54,1:10:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們在全境通緝布告里 ‎看到了你們所說的盧阿德爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've seen the APB for the woman you know as Lou Adell.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.95,1:10:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她跟照片里的這個人相匹配嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is she a match for the person in that photo?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.08,1:10:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎對 是啊 看起來像是她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Yeah, it sure looks like her.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.25,1:10:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-你能確信是她嗎 警長  ‎-就是她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-How confident are you, Sheriff? It's her.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.16,1:10:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎那第二個人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-And the second individual?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.08,1:10:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hang on one second.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.62,1:10:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你認得他嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you recognize him?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.29,1:10:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不認得 你是說這家伙也牽涉其中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Are you telling me that this guy is involved?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.29,1:10:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你知道這些人所處的位置嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have any intel on the location of these individuals?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.33,1:10:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-他們是不是在一起  ‎-我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Are they together? Well, I don't know if they're together.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.54,1:10:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我想他們要去老鷹灣 位于島的西側\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I believe is that they're headed to Eagle Bay, on the west side of our island.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.33,1:11:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們必須確保沒有平民前往那附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to make sure no civilians go anywhere near that location.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.16,1:11:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎設置路障 封鎖該區域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Set up roadblocks and cordon the area.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.04,1:11:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎還有個被綁架的小女孩 ‎她媽媽也在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a kidnapped girl and her mother out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.50,1:11:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-你等一會兒 ‎-什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hold. -Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.91,1:11:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這混蛋居然讓我等著 難以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Asshole put me on hold. Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.79,1:11:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太他媽不可思議了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Un-fuckin'-believable.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.00,1:11:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭金警長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sheriff Rankin? 
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.20,1:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎對 就是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.29,1:11:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎那個男性逃犯是美國特種部隊的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The male fugitive is US Army Special Forces,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.91,1:11:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎因多起謀殺平民案而被定罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}convicted in the murder of numerous civilians.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.45,1:11:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎那個女性是中情局的重點通緝目標\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The female is a high-priority target for the CIA.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.83,1:11:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎中情局 盧阿德爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The CIA? Lou Adell?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.54,1:11:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這項調查現在由美國執法官負責\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This investigation is now under the jurisdiction of the US Marshals.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.08,1:11:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎已獲授權使用致命武力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lethal force has been authorized.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.04,1:11:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎禁止任何人進入老鷹灣 ‎你們部門的人不準…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not allow any approach to Eagle Bay. -Not by your department, not-- 
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.25,1:11:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有一個被綁架的女孩和她的母親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There-- there is a kidnapped girl and her mother out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.45,1:11:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎別干擾我們執行任務 警長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay out of our way, Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.87,1:11:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎（急救箱）
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.45,1:11:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盧 抱歉 我來晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lou, sorry it took me so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.04,1:11:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我試著盡量往高處爬 但是…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I tried to get as high as I could, but…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.95,1:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎天啊 見鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Jesus. Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.70,1:12:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎天啊 好 等等 我來幫你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh God, oh God, oh God. Okay, wait, wait. Let me help. Let me help.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.83,1:12:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是他干的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Did he do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.37,1:12:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇呢 她沒事吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And Vee? Is she… is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.41,1:12:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她暫時沒事 他把她帶去燈塔了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's okay for now. He's taking her to the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.95,1:12:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎動作要快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do it quick--
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.50,1:12:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我正在弄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.75,1:12:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盡量用紗布填滿它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fill it with gauze. As-- as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.58,1:12:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-該死 ‎-來吧 深入一點 把傷口包緊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Oh shit. -Come on, deeper. -Really pack it in.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.87,1:12:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我正在弄 天啊 盧 ‎很抱歉 我把你拉下這趟渾水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'm trying. -Jesus, Lou. -I'm so sorry I dragged you into this.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.66,1:12:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎把手放在這里 用力按 我去拿些膠布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put your hand here. Right. Press down. Okay, good. I gotta-- I gotta grab some tape.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.62,1:12:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你聯系上警長了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah. Did you reach the sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.37,1:12:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-我也不確定 ‎-先別管了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Uh, I don't know. -Leave it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.00,1:12:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-等等 ‎-不用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Wait, uh-- -It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.16,1:13:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是我在小屋里找到的 ‎我原本想告訴你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I found those at the cabin. I meant to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.79,1:13:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你在說謊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.91,1:13:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎（嗨 媽媽 輪到我啦）
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.33,1:13:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這個留言不是給我的 對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This message isn't for me, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.33,1:13:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎都不是給我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}None of them are.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.29,1:13:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你說吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.25,1:13:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我要你親口說出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.25,1:13:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎說啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say it!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.04,1:14:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他是我兒子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's… my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.54,1:14:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我之前駐扎在伊朗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I was stationed in Iran,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.12,1:14:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎當時我必須接近一個極度危險的人物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had to get close to a very dangerous man.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.70,1:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎關系很親密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Very close.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.75,1:14:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.00,1:14:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我留著孩子是為了掩護我的臥底身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I kept the baby to keep my cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.20,1:14:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你是說菲利普嗎  ‎你的孩子 你是說你的兒子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean… you mean Philip? The baby? You mean your son?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.41,1:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎所以是怎么回事 在玩游戲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what is this? Some game?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.00,1:14:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你在捉弄我嗎  ‎怎么 是你告訴他我們在這里的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You fucking with me? What, you tell him where we were, or… -
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.16,1:14:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-不是 ‎-那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No. What-- what is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.16,1:14:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我不是在幫他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't helping him.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.58,1:14:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-我在幫你和小薇 ‎-別再騙我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I was helping you. You and Vee. -Stop lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.33,1:14:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎快他媽的告訴我真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Tell me the goddamn truth!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.50,1:14:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是我引你到這座島上來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got you to this island.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.08,1:14:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你大學的老朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your old friend from college?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.04,1:14:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎那個人告訴你奧卡斯島 ‎是個漂亮的世外桃源 房租又便宜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The one who told you about the beautiful secluded place on Orcas Island with the cheap rent?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.04,1:14:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是我讓她在街上假裝偶遇你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had her run into you on the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.66,1:14:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我原本想阻止菲利普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tried to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.75,1:15:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎于是我勒索中情局 ‎逼他們調查菲利普在薩爾瓦多的行為\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I blackmailed the CIA to force an investigation into what he did in El Salvador.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.41,1:15:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你以為是你救了我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You think you saved us?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.66,1:15:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我知道他最終會追蹤到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I knew he'd track you eventually.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.25,1:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你沒有救我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't save us.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.16,1:15:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是我帶著小薇離開了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got Vee away from him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.79,1:15:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我每天都照顧她 確保她的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I took care of her every goddamn day and made sure she was safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.37,1:15:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎就因為你 現在害小薇落在了他手上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now she's out there with him because of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.00,1:15:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你根本不是英雄  ‎你他媽的是個膽小鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're no damn hero. You're a fucking coward.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.12,1:15:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-這… ‎-那個男人的所有憤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Wow. -All that rage that that man felt.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.70,1:15:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他心里燃燒的全部怒火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the rage inside of that man that he felt,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.87,1:15:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎撒在我身上的怒氣 ‎全都是你一手造成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that he aimed towards me, is because of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.91,1:15:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不是每個人都適合當母親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not everybody is meant to be a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.91,1:15:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是啊 也許吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.37,1:15:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎但你原本可以更有人性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you could have been a little more human.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.83,1:15:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你每天都開車經過我們的拖車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You drove past our trailer every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.12,1:15:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盧 你開車經過自己的孫女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You drove past your own granddaughter, Lou.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.70,1:15:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你都沒跟她說話 ‎你一句話都沒跟她說過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't talk to her. You didn't speak to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.45,1:15:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你連看都沒看她一眼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't look at her.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.20,1:16:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎什么樣的人才會這樣對待自己家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What kind of person could do that to their own family?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.75,1:16:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎拜托 我們得繼續走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. We gotta keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.20,1:16:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎再也沒有“我們”了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There ain't no more "we."
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.62,1:16:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎漢娜 你不知道他們要去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah, you don't know where they're going.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.00,1:16:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你說了去燈塔 我會沿著海岸走過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said the lighthouse. I'll follow the coastline.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.70,1:16:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎不要獨自過去 這是陷阱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not on your own. It's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.16,1:16:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎求你了 至少這件事是我在行的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Please. There's one thing I'm good for.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.87,1:16:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎恐怕不是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.00,1:16:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你只會拖慢我的速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll just slow me down.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.87,1:18:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎賈克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Jax.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.50,1:18:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Lou!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.12,1:18:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.25,1:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎沒想過見到你居然會覺得高興\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never thought I'd be excited to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.70,1:18:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎凡事都有第一次 漢娜在哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-First time for everything. -Where's Hannah?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.08,1:18:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在去燈塔的路上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On her way to the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.95,1:18:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她的女兒呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And her daughter?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.00,1:18:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎已經在那里了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}-Already there with the… -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.58,1:18:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎跟綁匪在一起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}…the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.20,1:18:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他有武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's armed.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.45,1:18:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎非常危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.79,1:18:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎聯邦調查局也是這樣描述你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's exactly what the feds said about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.37,1:18:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你留在這里 ‎等道路暢通之后 我會派人來救你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You stay here. I'll send someone for you as soon as the road's clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.58,1:18:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎等等 天啊 先救我出去 ‎我在這里快喘不過氣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait. For fuck's sake, help me outside. I'm suffocating in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.50,1:18:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.41,1:18:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我來扶你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got this.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.45,1:18:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盧 你要告訴我 ‎為什么中情局要找你嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gonna tell me why the CIA's lookin' for you, Lou?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.08,1:19:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我用了手里掌握的一些證據\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I used some evidence I held onto.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.70,1:19:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎什么證據\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What kind of evidence?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.54,1:19:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎證明中情局參與了伊朗政變的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Documents. Proving CIA involvement in the coup in Iran.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.75,1:19:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我明白為什么他們很生氣了 ‎盧 他們正在趕過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can see why they'd be pissed about that. -Lou, they're on their way.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.29,1:19:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎見鬼 他們可不在乎殃及無辜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck, they won't care about collateral damage.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.54,1:19:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你得把漢娜和小薇救出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gotta get Hannah and Vee out of there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.37,1:19:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這傷口又崩開了 我會失血過多的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This thing starts up again, I'm gonna bleed out.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.37,1:19:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你能去拿急救箱嗎 我落在里面了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you get the first-aid kit? I left it in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.79,1:19:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.79,1:19:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lou! Lou!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.70,1:19:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎開什么玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.20,1:19:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lou!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.37,1:19:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.00,1:19:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-媽媽  ‎-小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Mommy! -Vee!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.25,1:19:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎快來 求你了 快來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come! Please, come!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.50,1:20:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-小薇  ‎-我在這里 媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Vee! -I'm here, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.87,1:20:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-在上面  ‎-我來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Up here! -I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.29,1:20:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.54,1:20:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.16,1:20:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎嗨 媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.29,1:20:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎嗨 寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.75,1:20:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們還擔心你不會出現呢 對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were afraid you weren't gonna show up. Weren't we, Vee?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.29,1:20:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.45,1:20:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她當然沒事 她和她爸爸在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course she's okay. She's with her daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.91,1:21:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎過來抱抱媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come, give Mommy a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.50,1:21:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎嘿 盧怎么樣了 她過來了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, how's-- how's Lou doin'? Is she-- Is she on her way?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.00,1:21:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎天啊 瞧瞧我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.33,1:21:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎這么多年了 我還在等我媽媽回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still waitin' for my mommy to come back after all these years, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.25,1:21:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎但我們確實需要等她來 了結這件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we do need her here to finish this.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.33,1:21:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我想給媽媽一個擁抱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanna give Mommy a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.58,1:21:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎菲利普 拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Philip, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.83,1:21:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎求你了 爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.04,1:21:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好的 小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, Vee.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.58,1:21:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎反正我們也在等盧 那就抱一下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One quick hug while we wait for Lou.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.37,1:21:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我好想你啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.95,1:22:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎游戲開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Game on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.91,1:22:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎爸爸 我能去洗手間嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daddy, may I go to the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.75,1:22:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎當然可以 小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course you can, Vee.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.83,1:22:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎但是上完就立刻回來 好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But hey… Come right back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.45,1:22:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎哇 盧對你的影響真不小嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow, Lou is really rubbin' off on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.45,1:22:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎來 把槍給我 ‎我們都知道你不會開槍打我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, just give me the gun. We both know you're not gonna shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.00,1:22:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你不了解我 菲利普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't know me, Phil.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.29,1:22:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-你從來都不了解 ‎-是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You never did. No?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.12,1:23:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎如果你要開槍打我 幾年前就動手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that if you were gonna shoot me, you would have done it years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.83,1:23:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我知道你跟我和盧不一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that you're not like Lou and me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.08,1:23:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你不是這種人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.08,1:23:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎換作是她 早就開槍了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, 'cause she would've shot me already.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.95,1:23:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎來吧 把槍給我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Give me the gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.75,1:23:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你拋棄了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You abandon me,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.45,1:23:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎偷走了我的孩子 現在還開槍打我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then you steal my baby from me, and now you shoot me?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.20,1:23:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你的話對我無效  ‎我不會再上你的當了 菲利普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That shit won't work on me. Not gonna work on me anymore, Phil.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.54,1:23:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我已經不怕你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not afraid of you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.33,1:23:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我不會讓你像傷害我一樣傷害我女兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I won't let you hurt my little girl the way you hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.45,1:24:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎漢娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hannah!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.08,1:24:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你還記得嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.58,1:24:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你還記得嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you remember…
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.37,1:24:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎感覺如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how it felt?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.70,1:25:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇 我們得跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vee! We have to run!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.50,1:25:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vee!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.41,1:25:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.70,1:26:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vee?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.00,1:26:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎游戲結束了 好嗎 來 小兔子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Game's over, okay? Come here, Little Rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.16,1:26:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們現在就得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We gotta go right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.87,1:26:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他有沒有傷害你 他沒傷害你吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did he hurt you? He didn't hurt you, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.62,1:26:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎躲起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh! Hide. Hide. Hide.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.41,1:26:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lou.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.33,1:26:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-漢娜 ‎-快來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hannah. -Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.87,1:26:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-We need to move.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.16,1:26:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Vee?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.50,1:27:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-我的槍 ‎-弄丟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-My gun. -Lost it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.83,1:27:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-刀呢  ‎-插到菲利普的手上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Knife? -Stuck in Philip's hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.45,1:27:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎試試從艙口出去 快去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try that hatch. Go, go, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.45,1:27:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎等等 你的外套卡住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Wait, your jacket's stuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.20,1:27:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Oh fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.54,1:27:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎把你推上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Push you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.54,1:27:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你得跑到海灘盡頭 有多快就跑多快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Run to the end of the beach. Run as fast as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.79,1:27:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-別離開我 ‎-我會來找你 我們爬不出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No! -I'll meet you there. -Don't leave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.00,1:27:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎現在快跑 去吧 小兔子 快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We won't fit. You gotta run now. Go, go, go, go. Run, Little Rabbit! Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.79,1:27:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎都混在一起了 沒法拆彈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's rigged. I can't defuse it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.79,1:27:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎如果改變頻道 或許能爭取一點時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could buy us some time if I can change the frequency.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.33,1:27:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你要去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Wait. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.16,1:27:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎咱倆當中有個真正的女童子軍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of us was actually a Girl Scout.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.37,1:28:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你還帶著對講機嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Do you still have the radio? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.58,1:28:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎也許終于能派上用場 去把艙口踹開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we can use it after all. Go bust that gate open.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.58,1:28:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lou?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.75,1:28:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們都在這兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.33,1:28:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們都在這兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.25,1:28:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我一直希望我們可以一起做這件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was hoping that we could all do this together.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.04,1:28:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎面對面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Face to face!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.00,1:28:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好讓大家都以恰當的方式做個了結\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So that we could end this… the right way.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.79,1:28:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎以恰當的方式做個了結\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}End this right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.33,1:28:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎全家人一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As a family.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.25,1:29:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎整個家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As a family.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.70,1:29:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎但有時候你無法一切如愿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But sometimes, you don't get what you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.83,1:29:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.20,1:29:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎媽的 見鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.08,1:29:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎操\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.75,1:29:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你他媽的讓我進去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck! You fuckin' let me in!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.75,1:29:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.70,1:30:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-該死 ‎-什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Oh shit. -What?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.41,1:30:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎中情局出動了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-The CIA's on the hunt.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.87,1:30:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎他們來找菲利普還是找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They comin' for Philip or you?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.37,1:30:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我和菲利普都別想活著出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They won't want either one of us to leave here alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.79,1:30:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Go, go. 
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.95,1:30:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-不 我只會拖慢你的速度 ‎-我不能把你撇下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No. -I'll just slow you down. -I'm not gonna leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.16,1:30:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盧 去把你的孫女 ‎帶到安全的地方 我會追上來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lou, go get your granddaughter to safety. I'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.50,1:30:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.08,1:31:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎小薇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Vee…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.75,1:31:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.33,1:31:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oof!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.00,1:31:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你是個勇敢的小女孩 你知道嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a brave little girl. You know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.62,1:31:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎幫幫我好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. Help me up, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.41,1:31:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好 聽我說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.91,1:31:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我要你去找一根木棍 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to go grab a stick, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.16,1:31:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盡量找一根最長的 去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The longest one you can find. Go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.91,1:32:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-媽媽  ‎-嘿 寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Mommy! -Hey, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.37,1:32:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎漢娜 對講機\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah. The radio.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.37,1:32:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎在我的口袋里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.25,1:32:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-來吧 ‎-幫幫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come on. -Help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.58,1:32:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎快 快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-All right. -Come on, go, run.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.87,1:32:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎漢娜 盡量把它舉高點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah, hold this up as high as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.00,1:32:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-你是在求救嗎  ‎-對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Are you calling for help? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.79,1:32:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是的 這應該能引起他們的注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. That ought to get their attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.54,1:32:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你趕緊走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.58,1:32:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎沿著這條路往鎮上走 把賈克斯帶上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take the road back towards town.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.62,1:32:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 把賈克斯帶來 - 你…你和我們一起來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}-Bring Jax with you. -You… you come with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.04,1:33:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎漢娜你要照料好你的孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hannah, you take care of your kid…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.41,1:33:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎而我會照料我的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take care of mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.20,1:33:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我在家給你留了封信 一定要找到它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I left a letter for you at my house. Make sure you find it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.20,1:33:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎走吧 小薇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Go on, Vee.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.33,1:33:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎可惡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.70,1:33:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎盧 你可別死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't die on me now, Lou.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.75,1:33:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你眼前的就是最重要的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything that matters is right here in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.91,1:33:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.41,1:33:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎去吧 快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go. Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.50,1:36:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎對不起 孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.16,1:37:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-嘿 小薇 ‎-嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hey, Vee. -Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.54,1:37:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你好 賈克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, Jax.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.41,1:37:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎嘿 你現在有兩條手鏈了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, you got two bracelets now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.20,1:37:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.54,1:37:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎就像你一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.83,1:37:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎（盧）
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.87,1:37:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎一條是為了紀念朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One's for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.62,1:37:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她突然就把這房子給了你和你女兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, out of the blue, she just leaves you and your daughter this house?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.37,1:37:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎是的 這間房子還有很多冷凍鹿肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, this house and a ton of frozen deer meat.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.70,1:38:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎門沒鎖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's open.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.62,1:38:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-嘿 漢娜 ‎-嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hey, Han. -Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.62,1:38:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你們好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.91,1:38:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我們還有幾個問題要問道森女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We had a few more questions for Ms. Dawson here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.16,1:38:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我沒有打擾你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope I'm not interrupting.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.25,1:38:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎漢娜 驗尸官那邊有個問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah, uh, coroner's got an issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.41,1:38:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你是親屬 需要你簽名 ‎才能給菲利普的遺體放行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're next of kin. He needs a signature to release Philip's body for burial.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.16,1:38:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Yeah. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.70,1:38:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎道森女士 盧阿德爾跟你提起過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ms. Dawson, did Lou Adell ever mention
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.62,1:38:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她在中情局任職期間的文件嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}anything about documents from her time in the CIA to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.33,1:38:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎要是提起過 她這特務就太菜了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She'd be a pretty shit spy if she did.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.95,1:38:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎如果你想起任何線索…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you think of anything…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.20,1:38:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你上次和上上次來的時候給過名片了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gave me a card last time you were here, and the time before that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.50,1:38:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎任何線索都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.50,1:38:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.29,1:38:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎-警長 告辭 ‎-很高興又見到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Sheriff. -Good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.08,1:39:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎別管他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Forget them.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.70,1:39:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎看來你們倆準備好去西雅圖了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like you two are ready for Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.33,1:39:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你都收拾好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, you're all packed up.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.04,1:39:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎對 差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, almost.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.41,1:39:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我想告訴你 追悼會辦得很體面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to tell you, you just did a beautiful job with the memorial service.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.70,1:39:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打住  不  是你干的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Stop. -No, you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.62,1:39:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想盧會很感激的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I think Lou would have really appreciated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.33,1:39:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎得了吧 那些真情吐露只會讓她作嘔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on now. All that sincere emotion would have made her puke.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.83,1:39:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她這人吧…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, well…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.50,1:39:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎她確實很有個性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-She was her own person. 
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.87,1:39:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我是說 有時候我很生她的氣 但是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean, sometimes, I'm just so damn mad at her, and then…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.75,1:39:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎有時候又很想念她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Other times I miss her.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.66,1:39:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎對家人的感情不都是這樣的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't that just how it is with family?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.62,1:39:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎我向來不是話多的人 ‎我就長話短說了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I've never been one for many words, so I'll keep this short."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.12,1:39:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎房子歸你了 拿去賣掉吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"The house is yours. Sell it."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.29,1:40:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎冰箱的肉夠賈克斯吃一個月 ‎還有給你一些現金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"There's a month's worth of meat for Jax in the freezer, and some cash for you."
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.91,1:40:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎人生沒有二次機會 ‎但有時候它允許你重新開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Life doesn't give you second chances, but sometimes it does offer a fresh start."
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.04,1:40:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎漢娜 你會好奇我為什么這么做 ‎為什么把這一切留給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Hannah, you're going to wonder why I did it." "Why I left this all for you."
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.50,1:40:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎簡單來說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"The simple answer is,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.45,1:40:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎你留給這個世界的東西 ‎會比我留下的東西更美好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you'll leave the world a better place than I did."
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.58,1:47:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‎字幕翻譯：楊宇航

